headline: 5 Top Artificial Intelligence (AI) Stocks Ready for a Bull Run
summary: Artificial Intelligence (AI) is proving to be a game-changing technology and with it, several companies are emerging as winners in this sector of the economy.  The stocks for many of these companies have already seen large gains.  Let's look at five AI stocks that could be set to continue to run higher in the coming years.
